snippet.title: Do Not Buy This Game - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist the game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1158190/Do_Not_Buy_This_Game/

Do Not Buy This Game is a Comedy Walking-Simulator where the character of the game's creator tries to push you away from playing the game because... well... it's not ready yet!

Make sure to like, comment, share and subscribe (and also wishlist the game!)
This can help out a lot when you have small upcoming indie games in development, and I'm trying to make this one of the funniest indie games ever made, 

Thank you ¡Lichi! for the Spanish subtitles!

#donotbuythisgame #narratedcomedy #walkingsimulator
